# 🏦 Loan Approval Prediction Project

This project predicts whether a loan application will be approved or not using Machine Learning.

## 📌 Project Overview

The goal of this project is to build a classification model that predicts loan approval status based on applicant details such as income, credit history, loan amount, etc.

---

## 📂 Dataset

- File: `train.csv`
- Target Variable: `Loan_Status`
- Features include:
  - Gender
  - Married
  - Education
  - ApplicantIncome
  - LoanAmount
  - Credit_History
  - Property_Area
  - etc.

---


## ⚙️ Steps Performed

1. Data Loading
2. Handling Missing Values
3. Encoding Categorical Variables
4. Data Visualization
5. Train-Test Split
6. Model Training (Logistic Regression)
7. Model Evaluation:
   - Accuracy
   - Confusion Matrix
   - Classification Report
   - ROC Curve
   - AUC Score